                                                                 .


 Just a ordinary UserStatus-display door that I guess EVERY /X-coder atleast
 once in their life-time have coded. I think it's hard to make something new
 and improved on these kind of status-doors. However, I made this door about
 1/2 year ago, but since it has never got released, I decided to drop it now.

 Hope you find it good enought for your board! :)


 I'll try to make some more good status-doors in the future, including graphs
 and other fancy stuff when runned.


           - - - --- ------[ lizard of megastyle! ]------ --- - -  -

@endnode






