 @{fg shine}To install...@{fg text}



 All you have to do is to copy each of the files in this archive to its
 belonging directory under "BBS:".

 That's all... (Simple isn't it? :)



 Megastyle! is not to held responsible if this program should cause any damage
 to your computer or lead to loss of data. It is provided as is, and is being
 installed and used on your own risk. There is no installer-script provided
 together with the UNREGISTERED versions of the Megastyle! productions!


